        "content": "## RAG: Data Ingestion to Supabase Vector\nPolls in each minute for new data that gets uploaded to drive, it then vectorize those information into efficient chunks, it uses openAI embedding model.\n\n**Pinecone vector store can also be used in place of Supabase**\n",
