    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## RAG: Pulling data from vector store for question answering\n\nAfter data ingestion we can decide to go for asking specific questions regarding the data ingested in the first workflow\nWe can use in-built n8n chat or for production grade systems we can use our own frontend and connect this chat model\nfor our own business purposes. We can feed our company data / meaningful internal data that the model will use later\nto answer on. Production grade systems might incorporate external database systems for better memory management.\n",
